{'category': 'Notice', 'content': '<tbody> \n <tr> \n  <td class="nhangjv" id="zoom" valign="top" td><br> \n   <div id="BodyLabel">\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="center">\n     <b>四川大学百脑汇奖学金评选通知</b>\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="center"></div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     为推动四川大学教育事业发展，鼓励四川大学优秀大学生努力学习、为社会多做贡献，百脑汇电子信息（成都）有限公司特于四川大学计算机学院（软件学院）设立“四川大学百脑汇奖学金”，现将2016年“四川大学百脑汇奖学金”评选有关事项通知如下：\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     <b>一、&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></b>\n     <b>奖学金评选范围及评选名额</b>\n     <b></b>\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     “四川大学百脑汇奖学金”用于奖励四川大学计算机学院（软件学院）的大二、大三年级在读本科学生，2016年共计10名，计算机学院、软件学院各5名，每人4000元。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     <b>二、&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></b>\n     <b>奖学金评选条件</b>\n     <b></b>\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     “四川大学百脑汇奖学金”旨在表彰奖励学业优异、品质优秀、社会实践能力突出的优秀本科生。申请者须具备以下条件：\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     1、思想政治素质高，得才兼备、勤奋学习的学生党员和学生积极分子。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     2、学风严谨，善于思考，具有一定学术能力、特别是具有解决问题能力的优秀学生，或是学业成绩在专业、年级名列前茅的优秀者。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     3、注重学习，理论联系实践，善于解决实际问题，并取得优异成绩者。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     4、有志于从事计算机、软件专业研究和工作的学生。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     5、同等条件下，家庭经济困难的学生优先。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     <b>三、&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></b>\n     <b>奖学金评选原则</b>\n     <b></b>\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     1、坚持公平、公开、公正的方式作为推荐和评选的原则。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     2、评选中严格掌握评选条件、严格执行遴选程序。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     3、除申请人学业成绩优异外，还需特别注重个人品德，积极参加社会公益活动，以促进心系祖国，服务社会。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     <b>四、&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></b>\n     <b>奖学金评选办法</b>\n     <b></b>\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     计算机学院（软件学院）组织成立“四川大学百脑汇奖学金”评审委员会（简称“评审会”）进行奖学金的评审工作并负责奖学金的管理及监督工作。具体评选办法如下：\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     1、评委会拟定评选通知并在基金会网站及学院网站公布。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     2、学生自己提出申请，经班级民主评议，学院学生科审议同意后，报评审会审核。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     3、评审会依据评选条件审核确定初选学生，公示无异议后，确定初步获奖者名单，并将相关材料报送百脑汇电子信息（成都）有限公司备案。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     4、百脑汇电子信息（成都）有限公司对提交的名单进行审定，最后确定获得奖励的学生名单。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     <b>五、&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></b>\n     <b>奖学金申请程序</b>\n     <b></b>\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" align="left">\n     申请学生自行下载并填写《四川大学百脑汇奖学金申请表》（见附件），并于2016年11月17日前将《四川大学百脑汇奖学金申请表》以及获奖情况证明、论文复印件、贫困证明等相关证明材料交到四川大学计算机学院（软件学院）学生科。请严格按照时间点报送，逾期视为自动放弃申请。\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\n     &nbsp;\n    </div>\n    <div style="TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT: 14px/19px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\n     \u3000\u3000\u3000附件：\n     <a style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 12px; TEXT-DECORATION: none" href="http://cs.scu.edu.cn/cs/rootfiles/2014/11/25/1416879426600496-1416879426602885.doc" target="CMSFILEINCONTENT">四川大学百脑汇奖学金申请表</a>\n    </div>\n    <br class="Apple-interchange-newline">\n   </div></td>\n </tr>\n</tbody>', 'time': '2016-11-14T03:17:00Z', 'title': '四川大学百脑汇奖学金评选通知', 'academy': '计算机学院', 'originURL': 'http://cs.scu.edu.cn/cs/xytz/webinfo/2016/11/1478149587692077.htm'}